  "keyFeatures": [
    "Generate fully functional Xcode projects from Bazel BUILD files with a single command",
    "Full support for Xcode features: indexing, debugging, runtime sanitizers, and SwiftUI Previews",
    "Focused Projects: include only a subset of targets in Xcode while unfocused targets build with Bazel",
    "Comprehensive Bazel rules support: rules_swift, rules_apple, C/C++/Objective-C, and custom rules",
    "Custom Xcode schemes with fine-grained control over build, run, test, and profile actions",
    "Multiple build modes: Build with Xcode (BwX) and Build with Bazel (BwB)",
    "Command-line API for performing Bazel commands in the same environment as rules_xcodeproj",
    "Support for iOS, macOS, tvOS, visionOS, and watchOS targets",
    "Cache warming support with xcodeproj_cache_warm_aspect",
    "Automatic and custom Xcode configuration management"
  ],
